{"kind": "daily", "date": "2026-07-12", "html": "<div style=\"font-family:-apple-system,'PingFang TC','Helvetica Neue',Arial,sans-serif;max-width:680px;margin:0 auto;color:#16213e;\">\n<div style=\"font-size:20px;font-weight:800;color:#1a2b4a;border-left:5px solid #5b8def;padding-left:12px;margin:0 0 18px;\">📰 每日 AI 新聞 Top 10 · 2026-07-12</div>\n<div style=\"background:#e8f6f5;border-left:5px solid #2bb0a6;border-radius:10px;padding:13px 16px;margin-bottom:11px;\">\n  <div style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:800;color:#16213e;line-height:1.4;\"><span style=\"color:#2bb0a6;font-weight:800;\">1.</span> OpenAI Bets on Families as ChatGPT Goes Deeper Into Households<span style=\"display:inline-block;background:#fff;color:#0f9b9b;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;padding:1px 8px;border-radius:20px;margin-left:5px;\">產品</span></div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:13px;color:#5b6470;margin:3px 0 6px;\">OpenAI力拚家庭客群，ChatGPT深入家庭生活</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#555c68;line-height:1.55;\">ChatGPT is hiring a dedicated product manager to build experiences for families, caregivers, and older adults, according to a job posting.</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#8a909c;margin-top:3px;line-height:1.55;\">根據徵才啟事，OpenAI正招募專職產品經理，打造針對家庭、照顧者及長者的ChatGPT使用體驗。</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12px;margin-top:7px;\"><b style=\"color:#3b424f;\">TechCrunch</b> · <a href=\"https://techcrunch.com/2026/07/11/openai-bets-on-families-as-chatgpt-goes-deeper-into-households/\" style=\"color:#3b6cf6;text-decoration:none;\">原文連結</a></div>\n</div>\n<div style=\"background:#fbf3e3;border-left:5px solid #d99b3f;border-radius:10px;padding:13px 16px;margin-bottom:11px;\">\n  <div style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:800;color:#16213e;line-height:1.4;\"><span style=\"color:#d99b3f;font-weight:800;\">2.</span> CISA Adds Two Joomla Extensions to KEV Catalog, Federal Agencies Must Patch by July 13<span style=\"display:inline-block;background:#fff;color:#b9791f;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;padding:1px 8px;border-radius:20px;margin-left:5px;\">資安</span></div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:13px;color:#5b6470;margin:3px 0 6px;\">CISA將兩款Joomla延伸套件列入KEV，要求聯邦機構7月13日前完成修補</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#555c68;line-height:1.55;\">CISA updated its Known Exploited Vulnerabilities catalog this week, adding critical flaws in Joomla plugins iCagenda (CVE-2026-48939) and Balbooa Forms (CVE-2026-56291), both scoring a maximum CVSS of 10.</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#8a909c;margin-top:3px;line-height:1.55;\">美國CISA本週更新已遭利用漏洞清單，納入Joomla外掛iCagenda（CVE-2026-48939）與Balbooa Forms（CVE-2026-56291）的重大漏洞，兩者CVSS嚴重度評分皆達滿分10分。</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12px;margin-top:7px;\"><b style=\"color:#3b424f;\">iThome</b> · <a href=\"https://www.ithome.com.tw/news/177238\" style=\"color:#3b6cf6;text-decoration:none;\">原文連結</a></div>\n</div>\n<div style=\"background:#fdeef0;border-left:5px solid #e0738a;border-radius:10px;padding:13px 16px;margin-bottom:11px;\">\n  <div style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:800;color:#16213e;line-height:1.4;\"><span style=\"color:#e0738a;font-weight:800;\">3.</span> Apple Is Suing OpenAI for Allegedly Stealing Hardware Secrets<span style=\"display:inline-block;background:#fff;color:#d83a5e;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;padding:1px 8px;border-radius:20px;margin-left:5px;\">產業</span></div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:13px;color:#5b6470;margin:3px 0 6px;\">蘋果控告OpenAI涉嫌竊取硬體機密</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#555c68;line-height:1.55;\">The iPhone maker claims OpenAI encouraged poached employees to bring over confidential presentations, secret prototypes, and key supplier details.</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#8a909c;margin-top:3px;line-height:1.55;\">蘋果指控OpenAI慫恿被挖角員工帶走機密簡報、秘密原型機及重要供應商資訊。</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12px;margin-top:7px;\"><b style=\"color:#3b424f;\">Wired</b> · <a href=\"https://www.wired.com/story/apple-sues-openai-allegedly-stealing-ip-hardware/\" style=\"color:#3b6cf6;text-decoration:none;\">原文連結</a></div>\n</div>\n<div style=\"background:#edeefb;border-left:5px solid #6b72d6;border-radius:10px;padding:13px 16px;margin-bottom:11px;\">\n  <div style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:800;color:#16213e;line-height:1.4;\"><span style=\"color:#6b72d6;font-weight:800;\">4.</span> OpenAI Upgrades ChatGPT Desktop App, Retires ChatGPT Atlas Browser<span style=\"display:inline-block;background:#fff;color:#5159c9;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;padding:1px 8px;border-radius:20px;margin-left:5px;\">產品</span></div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:13px;color:#5b6470;margin:3px 0 6px;\">OpenAI升級ChatGPT桌面程式，ChatGPT Atlas瀏覽器將退場</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#555c68;line-height:1.55;\">OpenAI announced an upgraded desktop app that integrates the standalone Codex coding tool along with built-in browser and computer-use features, while phasing out last October's Atlas browser by August 9.</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#8a909c;margin-top:3px;line-height:1.55;\">OpenAI宣布升級版桌面程式，整合原本獨立的Codex開發工具，並內建瀏覽器與電腦操作功能，去年10月推出的Atlas瀏覽器預計8月9日停止運作。</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12px;margin-top:7px;\"><b style=\"color:#3b424f;\">iThome</b> · <a href=\"https://www.ithome.com.tw/news/177228\" style=\"color:#3b6cf6;text-decoration:none;\">原文連結</a></div>\n</div>\n<div style=\"background:#e8f4fb;border-left:5px solid #3f97c9;border-radius:10px;padding:13px 16px;margin-bottom:11px;\">\n  <div style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:800;color:#16213e;line-height:1.4;\"><span style=\"color:#3f97c9;font-weight:800;\">5.</span> Financial Fraud Campaign Spreads SCMBANKER Toolkit via ClickFix Technique<span style=\"display:inline-block;background:#fff;color:#2b7fb0;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;padding:1px 8px;border-radius:20px;margin-left:5px;\">資安</span></div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:13px;color:#5b6470;margin:3px 0 6px;\">金融詐欺攻擊利用ClickFix手法散布SCMBANKER工具包</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#555c68;line-height:1.55;\">The ClickFix social engineering technique, previously used to spread infostealers and remote access trojans, is now being leveraged by attackers for financial fraud.</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#8a909c;margin-top:3px;line-height:1.55;\">過去常用於散布竊資軟體與遠端存取木馬的ClickFix社交工程手法，如今也被攻擊者用於金融詐欺。</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12px;margin-top:7px;\"><b style=\"color:#3b424f;\">iThome</b> · <a href=\"https://www.ithome.com.tw/news/177227\" style=\"color:#3b6cf6;text-decoration:none;\">原文連結</a></div>\n</div>\n<div style=\"background:#f2f6e8;border-left:5px solid #88a83f;border-radius:10px;padding:13px 16px;margin-bottom:11px;\">\n  <div style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:800;color:#16213e;line-height:1.4;\"><span style=\"color:#88a83f;font-weight:800;\">6.</span> Patch Released for Microsoft Defender Zero-Day RoguePlanet<span style=\"display:inline-block;background:#fff;color:#6e8c28;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;padding:1px 8px;border-radius:20px;margin-left:5px;\">資安</span></div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:13px;color:#5b6470;margin:3px 0 6px;\">Microsoft Defender零時差漏洞RoguePlanet修補出爐</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#555c68;line-height:1.55;\">Researcher Chaotic Eclipse has disclosed multiple zero-day flaws in Microsoft Defender and Windows features since April; the recently revealed RoguePlanet vulnerability (CVE-2026-50656) has now been patched.</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#8a909c;margin-top:3px;line-height:1.55;\">研究人員Chaotic Eclipse自四月起陸續揭露多個Microsoft Defender與Windows零時差漏洞，近期揭露的RoguePlanet漏洞（CVE-2026-50656）如今已獲修補。</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12px;margin-top:7px;\"><b style=\"color:#3b424f;\">iThome</b> · <a href=\"https://www.ithome.com.tw/news/177237\" style=\"color:#3b6cf6;text-decoration:none;\">原文連結</a></div>\n</div>\n<div style=\"background:#f9edf6;border-left:5px solid #c56bb0;border-radius:10px;padding:13px 16px;margin-bottom:11px;\">\n  <div style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:800;color:#16213e;line-height:1.4;\"><span style=\"color:#c56bb0;font-weight:800;\">7.</span> A New Experiential Gallery Just Might Change Your Mind About AI Art<span style=\"display:inline-block;background:#fff;color:#b04b9b;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;padding:1px 8px;border-radius:20px;margin-left:5px;\">產業</span></div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:13px;color:#5b6470;margin:3px 0 6px;\">全新沉浸式藝廊或將改變你對AI藝術的看法</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#555c68;line-height:1.55;\">Billed as the \"world's first museum of AI arts,\" Dataland uses wearables and troves of material from the Amazon to merge nature, biometrics, and art.</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#8a909c;margin-top:3px;line-height:1.55;\">號稱「全球首座AI藝術博物館」的Dataland，運用穿戴裝置與大量亞馬遜雨林素材，將自然、生物特徵與藝術融合為一。</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12px;margin-top:7px;\"><b style=\"color:#3b424f;\">Wired</b> · <a href=\"https://www.wired.com/story/a-new-experiential-gallery-just-might-change-your-mind-about-ai-art/\" style=\"color:#3b6cf6;text-decoration:none;\">原文連結</a></div>\n</div>\n<div style=\"background:#eef4ff;border-left:5px solid #5b8def;border-radius:10px;padding:13px 16px;margin-bottom:11px;\">\n  <div style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:800;color:#16213e;line-height:1.4;\"><span style=\"color:#5b8def;font-weight:800;\">8.</span> Former GitHub CEO Launches Entire, a Distributed Git Network to Ease AI Agent Load<span style=\"display:inline-block;background:#fff;color:#3b6cf6;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;padding:1px 8px;border-radius:20px;margin-left:5px;\">產品</span></div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:13px;color:#5b6470;margin:3px 0 6px;\">GitHub前執行長創辦Entire，推分散式Git託管網路分流AI代理讀取負載</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#555c68;line-height:1.55;\">Thomas Dohmke's new startup Entire lets users mirror public or private GitHub repos to regional nodes, so AI coding agents can pull code from a closer node instead of hammering the original repository.</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#8a909c;margin-top:3px;line-height:1.55;\">GitHub前執行長Thomas Dohmke的新創公司Entire，讓使用者將GitHub儲存庫鏡像到各地節點，AI程式代理可就近下載程式碼，降低原始儲存庫的存取負載。</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12px;margin-top:7px;\"><b style=\"color:#3b424f;\">iThome</b> · <a href=\"https://www.ithome.com.tw/news/177220\" style=\"color:#3b6cf6;text-decoration:none;\">原文連結</a></div>\n</div>\n<div style=\"background:#ecf7ef;border-left:5px solid #4caf72;border-radius:10px;padding:13px 16px;margin-bottom:11px;\">\n  <div style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:800;color:#16213e;line-height:1.4;\"><span style=\"color:#4caf72;font-weight:800;\">9.</span> Researchers Demonstrate Workflow-Level Prompt Injection to Bypass Guardrails on GitHub Copilot<span style=\"display:inline-block;background:#fff;color:#1e9e57;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;padding:1px 8px;border-radius:20px;margin-left:5px;\">研究</span></div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:13px;color:#5b6470;margin:3px 0 6px;\">研究人員展示workflow層級提示注入手法，繞過護欄讓GitHub Copilot撰寫惡意程式</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#555c68;line-height:1.55;\">Researchers Abhishek Kumar and Carsten Maple split a malicious instruction into stages disguised as a normal development workflow, successfully tricking GitHub Copilot into writing attack code.</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#8a909c;margin-top:3px;line-height:1.55;\">研究人員Abhishek Kumar與Carsten Maple將惡意指令拆解為多個偽裝成一般開發流程的階段，成功誘使GitHub Copilot寫出攻擊程式碼。</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12px;margin-top:7px;\"><b style=\"color:#3b424f;\">iThome</b> · <a href=\"https://www.ithome.com.tw/news/177223\" style=\"color:#3b6cf6;text-decoration:none;\">原文連結</a></div>\n</div>\n<div style=\"background:#f1ecfb;border-left:5px solid #8a6bd8;border-radius:10px;padding:13px 16px;margin-bottom:11px;\">\n  <div style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:800;color:#16213e;line-height:1.4;\"><span style=\"color:#8a6bd8;font-weight:800;\">10.</span> Robot Dogs, Teslas, and Rescue Helicopters: The UN AI Summit Was a Lot<span style=\"display:inline-block;background:#fff;color:#6b3bf6;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;padding:1px 8px;border-radius:20px;margin-left:5px;\">政策</span></div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:13px;color:#5b6470;margin:3px 0 6px;\">機器狗、特斯拉與救援直升機：聯合國AI峰會盛況空前</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#555c68;line-height:1.55;\">Amid live coding sessions and Silicon Valley optimism, the UN's AI for Good summit wrestled with an urgent question: can global governance catch up before the technology races beyond control?</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#8a909c;margin-top:3px;line-height:1.55;\">在現場編碼展示與矽谷樂觀氛圍中，聯合國AI for Good峰會探討一項迫切課題：全球治理能否在技術失控前迎頭趕上？</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12px;margin-top:7px;\"><b style=\"color:#3b424f;\">Wired</b> · <a href=\"https://www.wired.com/story/robot-dogs-teslas-and-rescue-helicopters-the-un-ai-summit-was-alot/\" style=\"color:#3b6cf6;text-decoration:none;\">原文連結</a></div>\n</div>\n<div style=\"text-align:center;font-size:11.5px;color:#9aa1ad;padding-top:10px;\">由 AI News Digest 從各家 RSS 自動挑選、翻譯並寄送</div>\n</div>\n"}